    <item>
      <title>由于销售疲软，库存压力，耐克在华尔街失去了粉丝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/nike-s-losing-fans-on-wall-street-as-weak-sales-raise-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耐克公司(Nike Inc.)本周面临着向投资者展示其计划提高销量的压力，此前该公司股价自20世纪80年代以来首次出现连续年度亏损，并继续落后于同行和大盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/nike-s-losing-fans-on-wall-street-as-weak-sales-raise-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:45:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦在船舶相撞后扣押影子舰队油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/denmark-detained-shadow-fleet-oil-tanker-after-ship-collision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦海事当局扣押了一艘本应运载俄罗斯石油的油轮，该油轮本月早些时候在丹麦水域与另一艘船相撞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/denmark-detained-shadow-fleet-oil-tanker-after-ship-collision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特航空将迁出利雅得，为新航空公司腾出空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/saudia-set-to-move-out-of-riyadh-to-make-room-for-new-airline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯的旗舰航空公司将逐步迁出利雅得机场，为该国最新的航空公司腾出空间，使其能够专注于吉达的主要枢纽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/saudia-set-to-move-out-of-riyadh-to-make-room-for-new-airline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:24:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯核供应链在全球峰会上获得通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/russia-s-nuclear-supply-chain-gets-a-pass-at-global-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国核监督机构警告说，没有快速的方法可以放松俄罗斯对核供应链的控制，并且威胁过早切断关系将损害全球能源市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/russia-s-nuclear-supply-chain-gets-a-pass-at-global-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:22:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
