      <title>卖空者再次加大对商业房地产的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/short-sellers-raise-bets-against-offices-as-fund-managers-grow-concerned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[地区银行面临的压力、美国写字楼价格持续低迷以及利率上升，使得基金经理纷纷看空他们最喜欢的行业之一：商业地产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/short-sellers-raise-bets-against-offices-as-fund-managers-grow-concerned</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
